pm2 glossary:
  pm2 start app.js --> This starts the application. it will run the application in the backgound of the server. 
  pm2 stop app_name_or_id --> This stops a running application. 
  pm2 restart app_name_or_id -->  This restarts am Application.
  pm2 list --> this will create a list of the curently working applications.
  pm2 info app.js --> this will show info about an application.
  
